Why are you young people so conserved?

51
00:03:40,390 --> 00:03:42,210
Xiao He,

52
00:03:44,090 --> 00:03:47,540
I'm so happy that Jiahui has

53
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,600
such a close friend like you.

54
