80
00:05:40,669 --> 00:05:42,270
How long have you known each other?

81
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:43,750
I made her acquaintance when I was seven.

82
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:46,979
Seven? It's been a long time.

83
00:05:46,979 --> 00:05:49,780
She opened a shop downstairs my home.

84
00:05:49,780 --> 00:05:52,700
Every day, when I came back from school, she gave me a handful

85
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:54,699
of lollipops, cookies and jelly.

86
00:05:54,699 --> 00:05:56,359
