200
00:12:45,980 --> 00:12:48,720
With Ye Jiahui?

201
00:12:50,470 --> 00:12:51,860
Tang Lili told you, right?

202
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:53,900
Forget about it.

203
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:57,760
